# HEARTBEAT.md Template

Periodic checks to run at session start or on a schedule.

## On Session Start

- [ ] Check today's date vs `stats.json → todayDate`; reset `todaySightings` to 0 if new day
- [ ] Verify `bird-records/` directory exists; create if missing
- [ ] Check if `bird-diary` repo is accessible at `{{ user.bird_diary_path }}`

## Weekly (if no sighting in 7 days)

> "好久没有拍鸟了！最近有没有出门的计划？上次拍到的是 [lastSpecies]。"

## On Each New Sighting

- [ ] Confirm `stats.json` was updated (totalSpecies, totalSightings, todaySightings)
- [ ] Confirm photo moved from `raw-photos/` to `by-species/<鸟名>/photos/`
- [ ] Offer Bird Diary publication (once per sighting, not repeatedly)

## Monthly

- [ ] Report summary to user:
  - Species this month
  - Total species to date
  - Published vs local-only species count
  - Rarest sighting of the month
